10 0 obj
<< /Length 1263 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (WHAT TO SAY \(AND NOT SAY\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 686.0 Td (SAY:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 670.0 Td (- "[Person] died. Their body stopped working and cannot be fixed.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.0 Td (- "It is okay to cry. It is okay to feel angry. All feelings are allowed.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.0 Td (- "This is not your fault. Nothing you did caused this.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.0 Td (- "I am sad too. We can be sad together.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.0 Td (- "I don't know why this happened. I wish I did.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600.0 Td (- "We will always remember [person]. They will always be part of our family.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 572.2 Td (DO NOT SAY:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 556.2 Td (- "They went to sleep" \(causes fear of sleeping\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 542.2 Td (- "God needed another angel" \(causes anger at God\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 528.2 Td (- "They went on a long trip" \(causes confusion/abandonment\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 514.2 Td (- "You need to be strong for mommy" \(suppresses grief\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 500.2 Td (- "At least they're not in pain" \(minimizes the child's pain\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 486.2 Td (- "Don't cry, they wouldn't want you to be sad" \(shames emotions\)) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
