12 0 obj
<< /Length 1174 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (CONVERSATION SCRIPTS FOR SPECIFIC LOSSES) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 686.0 Td (Death of a grandparent:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 670.0 Td ("Grandma/Grandpa's body was very old and tired. It stopped working.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.0 Td ("They loved you so much. Let's talk about your favorite memories.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 628.2 Td (Death of a parent:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 612.2 Td ("Mommy/Daddy died. This means their body stopped working forever.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 598.2 Td ("You will always be safe. I am here. [Other person] is here.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584.2 Td ("It is okay to feel anything. There is no wrong way to feel.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 556.4 Td (Death of a pet:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540.4 Td ("[Pet name]'s body stopped working. They are not in pain.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 526.4 Td ("It is okay to miss them a lot. They were an important part of our family.") Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 498.6 Td (Death of a peer/classmate:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 482.6 Td ("Something very sad happened. [Name] died. This was not normal.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 468.6 Td ("You are safe. Would you like to talk about how you feel?") Tj ET
endstream
endobj
