BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (GRIEF SUPPORT STRATEGIES) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 686.0 Td (Creating rituals:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 670.0 Td (- Light a candle on special days) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 656.0 Td (- Visit a meaningful place together) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 642.0 Td (- Make their favorite recipe on their birthday) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 628.0 Td (- Write a letter to them \(balloon release or burning\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 614.0 Td (- Plant a memorial tree or garden) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 596.0 Td (Daily support:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.0 Td (- Keep routines as normal as possible) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 566.0 Td (- Let them see you grieve \(models healthy processing\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 552.0 Td (- Give permission for ALL feelings \(including laughter and joy\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 538.0 Td (- Check in regularly but don't force conversation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 524.0 Td (- Expect grief waves at unpredictable times) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 506.0 Td (When to get professional help:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 490.0 Td (- Prolonged sleep or appetite changes \(2+ weeks\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 476.0 Td (- Talking about wanting to die or be with the person) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 462.0 Td (- Inability to function at school/home) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 448.0 Td (- Persistent nightmares or new fears) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 434.0 Td (- Self-harm or substance use) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 410.2 Td (Grief counselor: ______________________________________________) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 396.2 Td (Children's grief support group: _______________________________) Tj ET
